com.here.android.mpa.streetlevel

Interface StreetLevelCoverage.Listener

  • Enclosing class:
    StreetLevelCoverage

    public static interface StreetLevelCoverage.Listener
    Represents a listener to provide notification upon completion of a StreetLevelCoverage operation.

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      void onCoverageCheckCompleted(GeoCoordinate coordinate, int distanceToCoverage, StreetLevelCoverage.ResultCode result)
      A callback indicating that the StreetLevelCoverage.checkInCoverageZone(GeoCoordinate, int, boolean, StreetLevelCoverage.Listener) method has completed its operation.

    • Method Detail

      • onCoverageCheckCompleted

        void onCoverageCheckCompleted(GeoCoordinate coordinate,
                              int distanceToCoverage,
                              StreetLevelCoverage.ResultCode result)
        A callback indicating that the StreetLevelCoverage.checkInCoverageZone(GeoCoordinate, int, boolean, StreetLevelCoverage.Listener) method has completed its operation.

        Note: this callback is sent from a callback thread, not from the UI thread.

        Parameters:
        coordinate - The GeoCoordinate GeoCoordinate used in the coverage check
        distanceToCoverage - The distance (in meters) from the coordinate to the nearest coverage location.
        result - A StreetLevelCoverage.ResultCode indicating the result of checking for street level coverage
